                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-701-18470301 t18470301-701-punishment-54"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HACKETT</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18470301-701-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
